reviewText: Agns Varda is amazing!! This is a beautiful series of her work in California, definitely worth watching.  These are great for personal use or for teaching, I like to include Murs Murs and the Black Panthers in my introduction to art class.
Beautiful, subjective look at California during the late 60s and early 80s. Agnes Varda approaches her subjects with the same degree of love, admiration, and amusement.
